        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Secure Education for Americans Today Act of 2011 or SEAT Act of 2011 - Prohibits the provision of federal funds to institutions of higher education that admit illegal aliens.</p> <p>Prohibits such provision from being construed as denying federal student assistance to students attending such schools.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
